{"tid":1858253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[藍絲入] 如果政府要求警察止暴制亂","createTime":"2020-02-02T15:04:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T15:14:03.000Z","uid":81236,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1ca2d82f9c9309fe310dfcafa7e328d840d99f50","tid":1858253,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T15:04:13.000Z","msg":"但每間警局只分到<br />\n<br />\n槍 - 少量<br />\n<br />\n盾 - 少量<br />\n<br />\n防暴衣 - 少量<br />\n<br />\n但呢三樣野都係冷氣房啊蛇手上<br />\n<br />\n政府就唔停止輸入槍械比全港市民<br />\n<br />\n而家叫你出去止暴制亂，你做唔做？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />罷工，721啊sir有槍都調頭走<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />返工，然後等住葬浩園<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後一班腦殘就行出黎話警察罷工係逃兵<br />\n厭OT錢唔夠<br />\n返得呢份工就預左要死，係天職<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n果班腦殘就係你班藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"440857cfc59e9dbed50f10bc3960558119e5e967","tid":1858253,"uid":81236,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T15:06:11.000Z","msg":"藍絲沉默了？"},{"pid":"94c28ae49d3b61400b5624bd53cd47d8a5366f0d","tid":1858253,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T15:07:13.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80c4387c3d77f992fc1fa548039b9f33fce78309","tid":1858253,"uid":275648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T15:07:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"92543d63bcdc2816325d9fe3ee167001be6bce3e","tid":1858253,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80c4387c3d77f992fc1fa548039b9f33fce78309","tid":1858253,"uid":275648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T15:07:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T15:08:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><